# PyJWT Best Practices

## Overview
Best practices for JWT token management with PyJWT

## Rules
- Use strong, randomly generated secret keys
- Implement token expiration and refresh mechanisms
- Use `algorithms=['HS256']` for symmetric key algorithms
- Validate token claims on each request
- Use `leeway` parameter to account for clock skew in token validation 